##### Executables
fresh-options --bin
  fresh jasoncodes/dotfiles bin/loop                                                    # Loop over a script
  fresh jasoncodes/dotfiles bin/adduser                                                 # Adds User Account (for wemux)
  fresh jasoncodes/dotfiles bin/wemux/\*                                                # Wemux scripts
